    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rooms designed or used for sewing, which is the process of creating or mending clothing or other works by joining or decorating cloth, leather, or other flexible materials with thread by means of a needle. Sewing rooms may be furnished for hand sewing or machine sewing.</Note_Text>
